profile_summary:
I'm Lana Anvar, an AI and data science enthusiast with a strong passion for full-stack development. With a current focus on C++, Python, and R, I've established myself as a skilled programmer and have successfully contributed to numerous projects across various platforms. My extensive experience in languages, tools, and platforms, including but not limited to, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and MySQL, makes me an asset to any team.

Throughout my CS course at CUSAT, I've continuously honed my skills in machine learning, data analysis, and software development. With a strong background in programming and a keen interest in innovation, I am equipped to drive meaningful contributions in projects that touch on AI, data science, and software engineering.
